@startuml
title Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

hide circle
hide empty members
skinparam backgroundColor transparent

class User {
  +userId: String
  +name: String
}

class Role {
  +roleId: String
  +name: String
}

class Permission {
  +action: String
}

class Resource {
  +resourceId: String
  +name: String
}

User "0..*" -- "0..*" Role : assigned >
Role "1" -left- "0..*" Permission : grants >
Permission "0..*" -- "1" Resource : applies to >

note right of Role
Users are not assigned
permissions directly.
Permissions are grouped
into roles.
end note

@enduml